SELECT LISTAGG( COLUMN_NAME ,',') WITHIN GROUP(ORDER BY COLUMN_NAME ASC) LIST_COL_INS_TAR, LISTAGG( COLUMN_NAME || '= S.' || COLUMN_NAME ,',') LIST_COL_UPD, LISTAGG( 'S.' || COLUMN_NAME ,',') WITHIN GROUP(ORDER BY 'S.' ||COLUMN_NAME ASC) LIST_COL_INS_SRC FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS WHERE upper(TABLE_SCHEMA) =upper( CONCAT('lakehouse.', '${integration_schema}')) AND upper(TABLE_NAME) = upper('${integration_table}')
